  verified as unchanged since [GENERATION_DATE].

--- PATH B: PLATFORM VERIFICATION (If Available) ---

Visit: [VERIFICATION_URL]
Paste the packet hash into the verification form.
The system will return: MATCH or NO_MATCH.

